---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy · AroraMSP"
  description="AroraMSP privacy policy. What information is collected when you visit aroramsp.com and how it is used."
  page="privacy"
  canonical="https://aroramsp.com/privacy"
  ogTitle="Privacy Policy - AroraMSP"
  ogDescription="AroraMSP privacy policy. What information is collected when you visit aroramsp.com and how it is used."
>
  <section class="page wrap">
    <div class="page-head">
      <div class="sec-label">Privacy</div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="legal">
      <p>Last updated: 2026-05-10</p>
      <p>AroraMSP (aroramsp.com) is operated by Himanshu Arora. This policy
      explains what information is collected when you visit this site and how
      it is used.</p>
      <h2>Information collected</h2>
      <p>This site does not use tracking cookies, advertising pixels, or
      analytics services. No personal data is collected through browsing
      this site.</p>
      <h2>Contact forms and email</h2>
      <p>If you contact us by email, your email address and message content
      are used solely to respond to your enquiry. They are not shared with
      third parties.</p>
      <h2>Purchases and payments</h2>
      <p>When you purchase a product through our store, your name
      and email address are processed by Lemon Squeezy who acts
      as the merchant of record. AroraMSP receives your name and
      email address for order fulfillment only. Payment card
      details are never seen or stored by AroraMSP. Lemon
      Squeezy's privacy policy governs all payment processing.</p>
      <h2>Digital product delivery</h2>
      <p>After purchase, your email address is used to deliver
      your download link. It is not used for marketing purposes
      unless you explicitly opt in.</p>
      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>Order information is retained for accounting and legal
      compliance. Contact
      <a href="mailto:himanshu@aroramsp.com">himanshu@aroramsp.com</a>
      to request deletion of your personal data.</p>
      <h2>Governing law</h2>
      <p>This policy is governed by the laws of Malaysia.</p>
      <h2>Third-party services</h2>
      <p>This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect
      standard server log data including IP addresses as part of its
      infrastructure operation.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For any privacy questions contact
      <a href="mailto:himanshu@aroramsp.com">himanshu@aroramsp.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
